author: @rachela3869
text: Jaehyun looked so like a baby bird talking to an obviously extroverted American, but I'm proud of him for not shying away and having an English conversation without Johnny and/or Mark.  I think this might be the longest English I've heard Jaehyun speak.  He's so good at it, and has such a satisfying accent.  You can tell he's missing his members.  Jaehyun is so adorable.  He is also considerate and very sweet to the extra co-stars.  😎🥰💚🍑

author: @Amaralivilava
text: what do you mean this is the longest english, you have heard him speak. bffr

author: @rachela3869
text: @Amaralivilava  I mean consecutively.  He usually only says a few words or a short sentence when with the members.  Usually when English is spoken, Jaehyun relies on Johnny and Mark to do most of the talking. And I understand why, but he stretched himself and comfort level here.  The American guy, though very nice, asked a lot of questions and spoke a lot even for a native speaker. I'm just proud and excited Jaehyun didn't shy away from the conversation.   That's all I am saying. 😁😎👍
